'''J'an Ane Jinder''' was a [[Gender/Legends|female]] [[Jedi Guardian/Legends|Jedi Guardian]] of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]] and somewhat of an archaeologist as well.

==Biography==
Jinder traveled [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]], seeking out ancient or rare artifacts that might be of some interest to the [[Jedi Order/Legends|Jedi Order]].

On one such quest for an artifact from the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Malastare/Legends|Malastare]], J'an Ane wound up on [[Mrlsst/Legends|Mrlsst]], homeworld of the [[Mrlssi]]. In a Mrlssi [[Spaceport/Legends|spaceport]], while attempting to charter a [[Starship/Legends|starship]], she was offered a discount on the ship if she could solve the Mrlssi steward's riddle. The riddle involved the Mrlssi ship designers, their starships and three offworld clients. Using just a few pieces of information, J'an Ane was required to figure out which Mrlssi designed which starship for which client.

